name: Into the Woods (RachelEve)
description:
Your Nana has asked you to cut through the woods to get to her house faster, but what you both don't know is that in these woods live murderous Cult Members!

Use your trusty slingshot to successfully land three shots on the enemies to stay alive!

Survive for 45 seconds and you successfully make it to the end of the woods.

But be careful! If the enemies hit you three times with their spear, you will die!

Good luck.
